_sText:
The map is based on any other awp_maps .
It's a no-rush map , so you can't cross sides. This is typical for awp_maps.
There are two towers , 1 at each side. You can enter them by opening a door, and you can raise some defensive "things" in the tower to protect you.
I hope you like my map.
awp_matrix_beta
Made by Matrix (dragger40)
